# Cloud9Profile Project Documentation

## Overview

Cloud9Profile is a lightweight, responsive, and user-friendly platform to build resumes, portfolios, and check ATS compatibility. Supports Free, Professional, and Premium plans with a credit-based AI system. Designed for global users, SEO-friendly, and scalable.

## ðŸ†• Recent Updates

### Resume Templates (10+ Templates)
- **ATS-Optimized Templates**: Classic, Professional, Modern, Creative ATS
- **Creative Templates**: Vibrant Creative, Geometric Creative, Executive
- **Unified Field Fallbacks**: All templates now correctly display `Volunteering`, `Publications`, `Achievements`, and `References` sections
- **Print-Stable Layouts**: Creative templates maintain their two-column layout in PDF exports

### Watermark for Free Users
- PDFs generated by Free plan users display a **"Created with Cloud9Profile.com"** watermark at the bottom of every page
- Paid plan users (Professional, Premium) have no watermark

### Section-Wise ATS Optimization
- AI-powered keyword placement suggestions for specific resume sections (Skills, Experience, Summary)
- Missing keyword integration with smart section targeting

## ðŸŽ¯ Key Features

### ATS Resume Checker (NEW!)
- **File Upload Support**: PDF, DOC, DOCX with drag-and-drop
- **Advanced OCR**: 
  - **Hybrid OCR System**: Google Vision API (primary) + Tesseract.js (fallback)
  - Extracts text from scanned/image-based PDFs
  - Automatic detection of text-based vs scanned documents
- **Comprehensive Analysis**: 
  - Keyword matching with job descriptions
  - ATS compatibility scoring
  - Section detection (contact, education, experience, skills)
  - Missing keyword identification
  - Formatting recommendations
- **Email Reports**: Send detailed analysis to your email

## Tech Stack

* Frontend: Next.js (Page Router) + Tailwind CSS
* Backend: Node.js serverless API on Vercel
* Database: Supabase (Postgres + Auth + Storage)
* Hosting: Vercel
* Authentication: Email + OAuth (Google, LinkedIn, GitHub)
* AI Integration: OpenAI API or similar token-based AI for resume generation, JD optimization, cover letters
* OCR: Google Cloud Vision API + Tesseract.js

## OCR Configuration

The ATS checker uses a hybrid OCR approach for maximum accuracy:

1. **Google Vision API** (Recommended)
   - High accuracy for scanned documents
   - Requires Google Cloud account & API key
   - Free tier: 1,000 requests/month
   - See [GOOGLE_VISION_SETUP.md](./GOOGLE_VISION_SETUP.md) for setup

2. **Tesseract.js** (Fallback)
   - Free and open-source
   - No configuration needed
   - Good for basic OCR tasks

3. **Configuration**: Set in `.env.local`
   ```env
   OCR_STRATEGY=hybrid  # hybrid | google-vision | tesseract
   GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=./google-vision-key.json
   ```

## Authentication & Plans

* Multi-login: Google, LinkedIn, GitHub, Email/Password
* Plan types:
  - **Free**: 3 resumes, 1 portfolio, basic features, watermarked PDFs
  - **Professional**: Unlimited resumes, 5 portfolios, no watermark, advanced features
  - **Premium**: Everything in Professional + custom domain, interview prep, LinkedIn optimization
* Plan features defined in `lib/subscription.ts`
* Credit usage per AI action and add-on packs implemented

## Dashboard & UX

* ChatGPT-style, minimalistic, responsive, lightweight
* Sections: Resume overview, Portfolio preview, Credit usage, Plan upgrade CTA
* Light/dark theme optional
* Responsive across desktop and mobile

## Resume Builder

* Sections: Personal info, Education, Skills, Projects, Experience, Volunteering, Publications, Achievements, References, Languages, Interests, Declaration
* Templates: 10+ templates including ATS-optimized and Creative designs
* Drag & drop section reordering in preview modal
* Export: PDF (all plans), DOCX (Professional/Premium)
* **Per-page watermark** for Free plan users

## Portfolio Builder

* Preview only (Free), Full export (Starter/Pro), GitHub Pages export (Pro/Pro+)
* Controlled sections for Free/Starter
* Custom branding for Pro+

## AI / Credit System

* AI Resume Generation, Cover Letter, JD Optimization, Portfolio Suggestions
* ATS Auto-Apply: AI automatically integrates missing keywords into relevant sections
* Credits included per plan (Free 10, Professional 100/month, Premium 200/month)
* Add-on: Credit top-ups available ($5 for 100 credits)
* Credit consumption tracked in dashboard

## Public ATS Checker

* Free keyword match + % score for all users
* AI-based scoring for Pro/Pro+
* Email report generation to capture leads

## Screens & Navigation

* Auth: Landing / Signup / Plan Confirmation
* Dashboard: Resume & Portfolio overview, Credit usage
* Resume Builder: Editor, Preview, JD Optimizer, Export
* Portfolio Builder: Editor, Preview + Export
* AI / Credit Management: Dashboard + Modals
* Plans / Pricing, Profile / Settings, Public ATS Checker, Notifications / Help modal

## Frontend Page Router Structure

* `pages/index.js`: Landing / Home
* `pages/login.js`: Login page
* `pages/signup.js`: Signup page
* `pages/dashboard/index.js`: Dashboard overview
* `pages/dashboard/resume.js`: Resume Builder
* `pages/dashboard/portfolio.js`: Portfolio Builder
* `pages/dashboard/ats.js`: Public ATS Checker
* `pages/dashboard/credits.js`: Credit usage and refill
* `pages/plans.js`: Plan selection & upgrade
* `pages/profile.js`: Profile & settings
* `_app.js`: Global Tailwind, providers, auth wrapper

## Phase 1 MVP Tasks

### Backend

1. Authentication APIs (signup, login, OAuth)
2. Plan & Credit APIs
3. Resume CRUD APIs
4. Portfolio CRUD APIs
5. ATS Checker API (keyword match + email report)
6. PDF Export API

### Frontend

1. Auth pages (login, signup)
2. Dashboard (resumes, portfolio preview, credit info)
3. Resume Builder page
4. Portfolio Builder page
5. Public ATS Checker page
6. Plans & Profile pages

## DB Design (Supabase)

* Tables: Users, Plans, Resumes, Portfolio, Credits, ATS Reports
* Supabase Storage for PDF/Portfolio media
* Relationships and constraints implemented in Supabase

## MVP Phases

1. **Phase 1:** Free/Starter features (Resume Builder, Portfolio Preview, Public ATS Checker, Credit preview)
2. **Phase 2:** Paid features (Pro/Pro+, AI Resume Generator, Cover Letters, JD optimization, Portfolio Export, Multiple Resume Slots, Credit Refill System)
3. **Phase 3:** Global expansion (Multi-language support, Custom domain branding, Referral/Gamification, LinkedIn Auto-update, Advanced Analytics)

## Performance & Security

* Serverless backend on Vercel
* AI calls optimized to reduce token cost
* Duplicate account prevention for Free/Starter
* GDPR & global privacy compliant
* Secure file upload & export formatting

## Branding & Domain

* Brand Name: Cloud9Profile
* Domain: `cloud9profile.com` (or suitable TLD if unavailable)
* Global-friendly and SEO-optimized

## Development Workflow

* Branches: `main` (production), `dev` (integration), `feature/*` for tasks
* CI/CD via Vercel for frontend & backend
* Environment variables:

  * `SUPABASE_URL`
  * `SUPABASE_KEY`
  * `OPENAI_API_KEY`
* Recommended GitHub Actions for future automated tests

## Future Features

* Multi-language ATS scoring
* Referral & rewards system
* Advanced analytics dashboard
